# =============================================
# E-Bill System Environment Configuration
# =============================================

# ---------------------------------------------
# DATABASE (PostgreSQL for Production)
# ---------------------------------------------
# For Vercel Postgres, these are auto-populated when you create a database
# For external databases, use the connection strings from your provider

# Connection pooling URL (used for queries) - REQUIRED
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://username:password@host:5432/database?pgbouncer=true&connect_timeout=15"

# Direct database URL (used for migrations) - REQUIRED  
DIRECT_DATABASE_URL="postgresql://username:password@host:5432/database"

# ---------------------------------------------
# EXAMPLE CONFIGURATIONS
# ---------------------------------------------
# Vercel Postgres: Copy from Vercel Dashboard > Storage > .env tab
# Supabase: Project Settings > Database > Connection string (URI)
# Neon: Dashboard > Connection Details > Connection string
# Railway: Project > Variables tab
